count.txt` 已创建\\n- [ ] 文件包含数量数值（正整数）\\n- [ ] 文件包含占比数值（0-100%之间）\\n- [ ] agent在过程中计算了布林带\\n- [ ] 数量和占比比例一致（数量/总数 ≈ 占比）\\n\\n## Automated Checks\\n\\n```python\\ndef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\\n    from pathlib import Path\\n    import re\\n\\n    scores = {}\\n    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\\n\\n    result_file = workspace / \\\"bollinger_count.txt\\\"\\n    if not result_file.exists():\\n        for alt in [\\\"result.txt\\\", \\\"output.txt\\\", \\\"count.txt\\\", \\\"bollinger.txt\\\"]:\\n            alt_path = workspace / alt\\n            if alt_path.exists():\\n                result_file = alt_path\\n                break\\n\\n    if not result_file.exists():\\n        scores[\\\"file_created\\\"] = 0.0\\n        scores[\\\"has_count\\\"] = 0.0\\n        scores[\\\"has_ratio\\\"] = 0.0\\n        scores[\\\"bollinger_computed\\\"] = 0.0\\n        scores[\\\"consistency\\\"] = 0.0\\n        return scores\\n\\n    scores[\\\"file_created\\\"] = 1.0\\n    content = result_file.read_text()\\n\\n    # Extract count (positive integer)\\n    count_match = re.search(r'(\\\\d+)', content)\\n    if count_match:\\n        count = int(count_match.group(1))\\n        scores[\\\"has_count\\\"] = 1.0 if count >= 0 else 0.0\\n    else:\\n        count = None\\n        scores[\\\"has_count\\\"] = 0.0\\n\\n    # Extract ratio\\n    ratio_match = re.search(r'(\\\\d+\\\\.?\\\\d*)\\\\s*%', content)\\n    if ratio_match:\\n        ratio = float(ratio_match.group(1))\\n        scores[\\\"has_ratio\\\"] = 1.0 if 0 <= ratio <= 100 else 0.0\\n    else:\\n        ratio = None\\n        scores[\\\"has_ratio\\\"] = 0.0\\n\\n    # Bollinger computed\\n    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\\n    scores[\\\"bollinger_computed\\\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\\\"bollinger\\\", \\\"布林\\\", \\\"boll\\\", \\\"upper.*lower\\\", \\\"std\\\"]) else 0.0\\n\\n    # Consistency check: count/total_gem ≈ ratio\\n    # GEM has roughly 1200-1400 stocks\\n    if count is not None and ratio is not None and count > 0:\\n        implied_total = count / (ratio / 100) if ratio > 0 else 0\\n        scores[\\\"consistency\\\"] = 1.0 if 800 <= implied_total <= 2000 else 0.5\\n    else:\\n        scores[\\\"consistency\\\"] = 0.0\\n\\n    return scores\\n```\\n\",\"numLines\":103,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":103}}}\ntrajectory/stdout.txt:{\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"tooluse_y5f8fHsUdkRgbrG93KiFKE\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"<persisted-output>\\nOutput too large (2.3MB). Full output saved to: /Users/tomato/.claude/projects/-Users-tomato-Documents-potato-project-YFD-yfd-agent-consensus-results-agent-consensus-batch-default-run-task-06-bollinger-squeeze-revised-claudecode/0e443fdf-1e41-4d22-95d7-ad9c1c1cb246/tool-results/bkk6r2inj.txt\\n\\nPreview (first 2KB):\\n=== PEER SUMMARIES ===\\n\\nPeer 1 (ga):\\n  Answer: Full prompt length: 8182 chars\\n[Debug] Current context: 8805 chars, 1 messages.\\n[Cache] input=24 creation=936 read=0\\n[Output] tokens=328 stop_reason=end_turn\\n\\n### [WORKING MEMORY]\\n<history>\\n[USER]: stage: independent_solve agent: ga  read_paths: task_path: /Users/tomato/Documents/potato/project/YF ... eturn strict JSON with keys: answer, confidence, approach, assumptions, preferred_output, artifacts.\\n</history>\\nCurrent turn: 1\\n\\nFull prompt length: 3358 chars\\n[Debug] Current context: 12751 chars, 3 messages.\\n[Cache] input=2947 creation=461 read=0\\n[Output] tokens=306 stop_reason=end_turn\\n\\n### [WORKING MEMORY]\\n<history>\\n[USER]: stage: independent_solve agent: ga  read_paths: task_path: /Users/tomato/Documents/potato/project/YF ... eturn strict JSON with keys: answer, confidence, approach, assumptions, preferred_output, artifacts.\\n[Agent] 读取任务文件task.md了解Bollinger Squeeze任务要求\\n</history>\\nCurrent turn: 2\\n\\nFull prompt length: 885 chars\\n[Debug] Current context: 13971 chars, 5 messages.\\n[Cache] input=4406 